          <h2 class="date-header">
           <span>
            October 12, 2018
           </span>
          </h2>
          <div class="date-posts">
           <div class="post-outer">
            <div class="post hentry uncustomized-post-template" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
             <meta content="35771364" itemprop="blogId"/>
             <meta content="6423227931862813530" itemprop="postId"/>
             <a name="6423227931862813530">
             </a>
             <h3 class="post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">
              <a href="https://news-rac.berkeley.edu/2018/10/nih-seeks-comments-on-proposed-data.html">
               NIH Seeks Comments on Proposed Data Management and Sharing Policy
              </a>
             </h3>
             <div class="post-header">
              <div class="post-header-line-1">
              </div>
             </div>
             <div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-6423227931862813530" itemprop="description articleBody">
              The National Institutes of Health issued
              <a href="https://grants.nih.gov/grants/guide/notice-files/NOT-OD-19-014.html">
               Request
 for Information (RFI) on Proposed Provisions for a Draft Data 
Management and Sharing Policy for NIH Funded or Supported Research 
(NOT-OD-19-014)
              </a>
              to solicit public input on proposed key provisions that could serve as the foundation for a future NIH policy for data management and sharing.  The feedback will help NIH develop a draft policy.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              NIH is
              <a href="https://osp.od.nih.gov/provisions-data-managment-sharing/">
               accepting comments
              </a>
              through December 10, 2018.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              NIH is hosting a
              <a href="https://nih.webex.com/mw3200/mywebex/default.do?service=1&amp;siteurl=nih&amp;nomenu=true&amp;main_url=%2Fmc3200%2Fe.do%3Fsiteurl%3Dnih%26AT%3DMI%26EventID%3D733056507%26UID%3D544613017%26Host%3DQUhTSwAAAARONjg2eUNgoW9gHCmk7-Kw4WL-h9YBLwRmch4VGXfK6HzCQ_QJPg0WYEAVMlrRukbkOJ5LpzGS3aG_kuRihYJN0%26FrameSet%3D2%26MTID%3Dme63907249242f0cca842d90e8d4493ef">
               webinar
              </a>
              on the proposed key provisions on November 7, 2018, from 8:30 a.m. to 10:00am PT.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              For more information, see
              <br/>
              <ul>
               <li>
                <a href="https://grants.nih.gov/grants/guide/notice-files/NOT-OD-19-014.html">
                 Request for Information (RFI) on Proposed Provisions for a Draft Data Management and Sharing Policy for NIH Funded or Supported Research (NOT-OD-19-014)
                </a>
                ,
               </li>
               <li>
                <a href="https://osp.od.nih.gov/2018/10/11/nih-seeks-public-comment-proposed-provisions-future-draft-data-management-sharing-policy/">
                 NIH Seeks Public Comment on Proposed Provisions for a Future Draft Data Management and Sharing Policy
                </a>
                , and
               </li>
               <li>
                <a href="https://osp.od.nih.gov/2018/10/10/data-sharing-renaissance-music-ears/">
                 A Data Sharing Renaissance: Music to My Ears!
                </a>
                .
               </li>
              </ul>
              <div style="clear: both;">
