          <h2 class="date-header">
           <span>
            September 14, 2018
           </span>
          </h2>
          <div class="date-posts">
           <div class="post-outer">
            <div class="post hentry uncustomized-post-template" itemprop="blogPost" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
             <meta content="35771364" itemprop="blogId"/>
             <meta content="9133149042048075415" itemprop="postId"/>
             <a name="9133149042048075415">
             </a>
             <h3 class="post-title entry-title" itemprop="name">
              <a href="https://news-rac.berkeley.edu/2018/09/opportunity-to-influence-nsf-priorities.html">
               Opportunity to Influence NSF Priorities: NSF 2026 Idea Machine
              </a>
             </h3>
             <div class="post-header">
              <div class="post-header-line-1">
              </div>
             </div>
             <div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-9133149042048075415" itemprop="description articleBody">
              The National Science Foundation is encouraging researchers, the public, and other interested stakeholders to contribute to NSF’s mission to support basic research and enable new discoveries that drive the U.S. economy, enhance national security, and advance knowledge to sustain U.S. global leadership in science and engineering.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              The
              <a href="https://www.nsf.gov/news/special_reports/nsf2026ideamachine/index.jsp">
               NSF 2026 Idea Machine
              </a>
              is a competition to help set the U.S. agenda for fundamental research in science and engineering. Participants can earn prizes and receive public recognition by suggesting the pressing research questions that need to be answered in the coming decade, the next set of “Big Ideas” for future investment by NSF.
              <a href="https://www.nsf.gov/news/special_reports/nsf2026ideamachine/index.jsp">
               Submit entries
              </a>
              by October 26, 2018.
              <br/>
              <br/>
              <hr/>
              September 13, 2018 CALmessages notice:
              <a href="https://calmessages.berkeley.edu/archives/message/60527">
               Opportunity to influence future NSF priorities: The NSF 2026 Idea Machine
              </a>
              <div style="clear: both;">
              </div>
             </div>
